tags: i wrote out most if this image description like a week ago and then accidentally clicked off it and lost all my progress
summary:
Some Pokemon gijinkas I did for a sort of art trade with @wiittyusername !
[Image description: four digital drawings of Pokémon...
body:
Some Pokemon gijinkas I did for a sort of art trade with @wiittyusername !

[Image description: four digital drawings of Pokémon as humans, next to their Pokémon counterpart.

The first image is of Wooloo, a sheep-like creature. As a human, she is a dark skinned, chubby girl with off-white hair in two medium-length braids. She is wearing a light brown, sleeveless shirt-dress, a fluffy off-white vest, black tights with hearts on them and light brown boots tied with pink ribbon. She is holding a basket of flowers, and smiling at the viewer in a reclined pose.

The second image is of Lilligant, a plant-like humanoid creature with a crown. As a human, she is a pale skinned, chubby girl with green hair in a bun. She is wearing a yellow jacket with a stomacher, with translucent green sleeves hanging from her shoulder to her wrist, and a green ribbon around her waist that’s tied in a bow at the back. She has a long, light green skirt, golden shoes that curl up at the toe and she has a golden crown with thick orange petals surrounding it. She is looking upwards as she gestures with both hands.

The third image is of Skitty, a yellow and pink cat-like creature. As a human, she is a light skinned, chubby girl with short, light pink hair in a high ponytail and freckles. She is wearing a light pink cropped cardigan over a light yellow vest top, and dark purple shorts. She has dark purple trainers and light pink knee high socks with light yellow spots. She is looking over her shoulder with one hand on her hip.

The fourth image is of Dragonair, a blue snake-like creature with a horn, wings on the side of its head and gems at its throat and the end of its tail. As a human, she is a pale skinned, thin woman, with knee length light blue hair. She is wearing a long, sleeveless, white dress with a light blue translucent overlay that is split down the middle and trails behind her. She has a white choker with a blue gem with two light blue translucent loops hanging around her upper arms. She has a white circlet with a horn on the front and wings on the sides, light blue high heels with white horns and wing patterns on the side, and she is holding a light blue staff with a large blue gem at the top. She is standing straight with one hand holding her staff to her side, and the other holding part of her dress’ overlay out.]
